  popular javascript module standards
  
  
  1. AMD
  2. commonJS
  
  
  ---------------------------------
  
  
  commonJS
  
  notes:
  
  --> every .js file is an module
  --> we need to export explicitly to others modules with 'module.export'
  --> import with 'require'
  
  
  NodeJS uses 'commonJS' as an default module-standard at present.
  
